backups/

# Claude Code local settings + skills (per-machine, do not commit)
.claude/

# Native folders — regenerated by `expo prebuild --clean` on every build.
# All native config lives in app.config.js. See docs/DEV_PROD_ENVIRONMENTS.md.
ios/
android/
